            "heading": "<strong>Eligibility for Refunds</strong>",
            "page_content": "",
            "description": "<p>You may be eligible for a refund under the following conditions</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Non-working Keys:</strong> If the game key you purchased is found to be invalid or does not work, despite following the proper activation instructions.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Duplicate Purchases:</strong> If you accidentally purchased the same game key more than once, provided the duplicate key has not been downloaded.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "text_aA3N6w": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>Conditions for Refunds</strong>",
            "page_content": "",
            "description": "<p>To qualify for a refund, the following conditions must be met:</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Proof of Issue:</strong> You must provide a clear explanation and evidence of the issue you are experiencing with the game key.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Timely Request:</strong> Refund requests must be made within 14 days of purchase. Requests made after this period will not be eligible for a refund.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Unredeemed and Non-Downloaded Keys:</strong> The game key must not have been redeemed, used, or downloaded. Keys that have already been activated or downloaded are not eligible for a refund.</li></ul><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_rG8LqH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>Non-Refundable Situations</strong>",
            "page_content": "",
            "description": "<p>We do not offer refunds in the following situations:</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Compatibility Issues:</strong> If your system does not meet the game’s requirements, it is your responsibility to verify this before purchasing.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Regional Restrictions:</strong> If the game key is region-locked and you attempt to use it in a non-supported region, unless the restriction was not clearly mentioned at the time of purchase.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Downloaded Keys:</strong> If the game key has been downloaded and thus seen by users, a refund will not be possible.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "text_Rk3qJA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>How to Request a Refund</strong>",
            "page_content": "",
            "description": "<p>If you meet the criteria for a refund, follow these steps to request one</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Contact Support:</strong> Email our customer support at info@gamesporium.com or use the contact form on our website.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Provide Details:</strong> Include your order number, the game key in question, and a detailed description of the issue.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Await Response:</strong> Our support team will review your request and respond within 48 hours.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "text_mYNCdE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>Refund Process</strong>",
            "page_content": "",
            "description": "<p>Once your refund request is approved</p><p></p><ul><li><strong>Processing Time:</strong> Refunds are typically processed within 5-7 business days.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Payment Method:</strong> Refunds will be issued to the original payment method used during the purchase.</li></ul><p></p><ul><li><strong>Confirmation:</strong> You will receive an email confirmation once the refund has been processed.</li></ul>"
